%% Diagram: Draft autosave + recovery lifecycle
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Form runtime
    participant W as Watcher (debounced)
    participant DB as IndexedDB
    participant API as Backend

    Note over F,DB: Page load — recovery phase
    F->>DB: get(formId)
    DB-->>F: { data, savedAt } or null
    alt draft exists and not stale
        F-->>U: prompt "Restore draft?"
        U->>F: restore | discard
    end

    Note over F,W: Editing phase — autosave
    loop on every keystroke
        U->>F: input
        F->>W: notify(values)
    end
    W-->>DB: put(formId, snapshot) (after 2s idle)

    Note over F,API: Submit phase
    U->>F: submit
    F->>API: POST submission
    API-->>F: 2xx
    F->>DB: delete(formId)
